BBBF
.author
Johan Eliasson
Safe Hex International member 
.version
101_31
.description
The Bootblock.library and brainfile is now used by several programs e. g.:
D-Copy 3.1, X-Copy from april 93 and VirusChecker from version 6.29.
Intended for use by programmers of anti-virus utilities, diskcopy program,
directory utilities, disk packers and for whoever who wants to check the
bootblock of some device.  The library has some easy-to-use functions to
read the brain-file, and to check a bootblock with it.  An update to
version 0.95 beta on disk 797.  This brainfile now recognizes 163 different
boot viruses and about 70 boot virus clones.  Includes sample source.  
